about: Hi! I'm Vaishnavi, a passionate Software Developer on an exciting journey through the world of code and technology. I specialize in transforming ideas into responsive, dynamic web experiences that captivate users. My expertise spans across HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, JavaScript, PHP, CodeIgniter, Laravel, Python, Django, NodeJS, ReactJS, ExpressJS, MySQL, MSSQL, and version management tools like Git and GitHub. This diverse skill set allows me to tackle a wide range of projects, from building robust RESTful APIs for mobile applications to designing efficient and scalable web applications. I completed my Bachelor's in Computer Engineering from 2018 to 2022. My journey as a software developer is a never-ending adventure, and I am loving every moment of it. I am committed to excellence and continuous improvement. I look forward to contributing to innovative projects and being part of a team that values creativity, collaboration, and growth.
